name: Montenegro Gov't Day
description:
Montenegro and Zuzalu citizens share ideas for how we can work together to create a brighter future for Montenegro and Zuzalu.

The Prime Minister of Montenegro and other government officials will be visiting Zuzalu to learn more about us and share ideas for how we can work together to create a brighter future for Montenegro and Zuzalu. We will cover topics like how Montenegro can be a Talent, Education, Healthcare and Blockchain center of the world.


Detailed Schedule: https://zuzalu.notion.site/zuzalu/Montenegro-Day-May-15-34da371526a74eceb884de14416df115
